{"tid":794810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"走出MeToo陰霾 呂麗瑤100米欄奪銅","createTime":"2018-08-26T13:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T15:49:42.000Z","uid":1159,"like":6,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb9ed6c5ff31df44471f6688f90746d97ac5648","tid":794810,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>【雅加達亞運】走出MeToo陰霾 呂麗瑤100米欄奪銅</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180826/large/1535289618_7488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F1535289618_7488.jpg&h=112c6a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呂麗瑤（前）於女子100米欄奪銅。<br />\n<br />\n雅加達亞運會田徑賽事，香港「欄后」因在Facebook公開聲稱被前教練性侵犯，但其後一直拒絕報警而被網民質疑發動網絡公審遭抨擊的港隊田徑隊選手呂麗瑤成功走出「#MeToo」陰霾，奪得港隊今屆亞運田徑項目首面獎牌！去年曾公開年幼時遭性侵的「呂神」呂麗瑤，今日在雅加達亞運女子100米欄決賽，跑出個人最佳的13秒42奪得一面銅牌，南韓的Jung Hyelim以13秒20得冠軍，亞軍是印尼的Emilia Nova，時間是13秒33。<br />\n<br />\n周日的女子100米欄決賽，呂麗瑤雖然身處第一線，但起步最先彈出處於領先位置，其後雖然被南韓及印尼選手趕過，但仍以13秒42力壓中國選手王逗奪得銅牌，更比自己的個人最佳時間13秒44快0.02秒。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的瑤瑤是第二次參加亞運會，上屆仁川亞運，她不入決賽，但經過四年的磨鍊後，尤其近年跟了教練鄧漢昇，她的跨欄時間日益進步，她曾於今年五月香港田徑錦標賽中，跑出13秒44的個人最佳，今次在亞運會更進一步，跑出新的個人最佳13秒42。<br />\n記者：徐嘉華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180826/58610878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F58610878&d=Y%2FW%2FCsZJIoYQ15%2FbMY8nJxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=70a10025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F58610878&h=7140a2de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180826/58610878</a>"},{"pid":"20d52d325c7185c9ca723575c1d42793bf7b984d","tid":794810,"uid":8572,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人上過麗瑤？？？"},{"pid":"69356aced52bf0480d427288b6cf8e372aaebd89","tid":794810,"uid":12021,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8d6cc4dbb5d6608d5729a1fcbae7324ba913c26","tid":794810,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"後面條女著長褲跑？"},{"pid":"ff74e6fda9589ff6c40b54f16cd2847ade8336a1","tid":794810,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8d6cc4dbb5d6608d5729a1fcbae7324ba913c26","tid":794810,"uid":47663,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"後面條女著長褲跑？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"似係伊斯蘭嗰啲人"},{"pid":"9cb46b8c7d2bdbb4fe4fb71f5b4c2f9c55517808","tid":794810,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"066b43c8bfd2b2c249f204314baa129f3fe21f81","tid":794810,"uid":36417,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"因在Facebook公開聲稱被前教練性侵犯，但其後一直拒絕報警而被網民質疑發動網絡公審遭抨擊的港隊田徑隊選手呂麗瑤"},{"pid":"477a3526629d392bbbeed93e19f749e52d4beb93","tid":794810,"uid":157362,"like":10,"dislike":15,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a6a478041add5e43304e00428176b6bf1819378","tid":794810,"uid":51932,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"477a3526629d392bbbeed93e19f749e52d4beb93","tid":794810,"uid":157362,"like":10,"dislike":15,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:15:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"你俾佢metoo睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28d3cb081d5cfe76080bd42286eaaaeb9d5b977","tid":794810,"uid":34854,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"一句說話令教練人生賠上了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e922356cdbb0c47419bf21d56d930e1f2a9db5","tid":794810,"uid":78394,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"呂：多謝連登仔，再踩我多d啦"},{"pid":"e160377d18a482412656ecd51f761dcf7d53685d","tid":794810,"uid":69213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c5800f5a40b475031ddb928665b93c8e4f2f6f3","tid":794810,"uid":144466,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"尤其近年跟了教練鄧漢昇<br />\n<br />\n鄧教練要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56d8d00a82506b3acdb3421a1acfee26c78d8f6","tid":794810,"uid":144466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"066b43c8bfd2b2c249f204314baa129f3fe21f81","tid":794810,"uid":36417,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"因在Facebook公開聲稱被前教練性侵犯，但其後一直拒絕報警而被網民質疑發動網絡公審遭抨擊的港隊田徑隊選手呂麗瑤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"因瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"631443f7d8d6e2dd840d829ff3d1c7ecf8f37487","tid":794810,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:10:43.000Z","msg":"想問me too加銅牌<br />\n可以有幾多廣告費？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fcdae822ee41e70267a074db1d353a9ce1a794","tid":794810,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"條腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72baa11ed532b58ba1bd044f1fac563eb4dd061","tid":794810,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180802/58514312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58514312&d=Y%2FW%2FCsZJIoYQ15%2FbMY8nJxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=33b4123e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58514312&h=1f7c81e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180802/58514312</a><br />\n<br />\n曾任田徑教練的77歲退休人士黃恆，涉嫌於8年前在大埔非禮一名女子。案件今預審。辯方透露控方調查期間曾聯絡被告過去10年曾任教中學的教師或校長，涉及超過十間學校，查詢該校曾否犯類似非禮，答案是否定。據了解，辯方於是要求控方傳召有關老師或校長出庭讓辯方盤問，但遭拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n77歲被告黃恆被控於2009年9月1日至2010年4月8日期間某一天，在大埔非禮X，控方以代號W.H.稱呼黃。<br />\n控方將申請事主以視像系統作供<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官練錦鴻主動謂：「我諗住我做單嘢，有冇反對？」控辯雙方沒反對，<span style=\"color: red;\">案件排期於9月26日開審，預計審理兩天</span>。控方明言會申請事主透過視像系統作供，雙方押後期間會另排期爭拗，黃續保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n控方今呈上同意案情，透露審訊時將傳召3名證人，包括事主、事主朋友及中學老師，其中老師的證供會談及被告與事主之間的關係。練官聞言問：「被告認識受害人，冇得拗，係咪？」控方另明言會申請事主透過閉路電視作供，若失敗將申請事主在屏風後作供，控辯雙方另排期處理。<br />\n<br />\n至於辯方要求控方傳召被告曾任教的十間學校校長和教師等人，控方回應有關資料與本案無關。練官不同意，謂有關資料與被告的犯案傾向性有關，但補充謂，即使「係negative（否定），唔代表今次佢冇做」。練官指，最終是否傳召或同意有關資料，全由控方決定。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：FLCC1971/18】"},{"pid":"f619e6ff3870c4397507fe355730096395e19487","tid":794810,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb9ed6c5ff31df44471f6688f90746d97ac5648","tid":794810,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>【雅加達亞運】走出MeToo陰霾 呂麗瑤100米欄奪銅</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180826/large/1535289618_7488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180826%2Flarge%2F1535289618_7488.jpg&h=112c6a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呂麗瑤（前）於女子100米欄奪銅。<br />\n<br />\n雅加達亞運會田徑賽事，香港「欄后」因在Facebook公開聲稱被前教練性侵犯，但其後一直拒絕報警而被網民質疑發動網絡公審遭抨擊的港隊田徑隊選手呂麗瑤成功走出「#MeToo」陰霾，奪得港隊今屆亞運田徑項目首面獎牌！去年曾公開年幼時遭性侵的「呂神」呂麗瑤，今日在雅加達亞運女子100米欄決賽，跑出個人最佳的13秒42奪得一面銅牌，南韓的Jung Hyelim以13秒20得冠軍，亞軍是印尼的Emilia Nova，時間是13秒33。<br />\n<br />\n周日的女子100米欄決賽，呂麗瑤雖然身處第一線，但起步最先彈出處於領先位置，其後雖然被南韓及印尼選手趕過，但仍以13秒42力壓中國選手王逗奪得銅牌，更比自己的個人最佳時間13秒44快0.02秒。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的瑤瑤是第二次參加亞運會，上屆仁川亞運，她不入決賽，但經過四年的磨鍊後，尤其近年跟了教練鄧漢昇，她的跨欄時間日益進步，她曾於今年五月香港田徑錦標賽中，跑出13秒44的個人最佳，今次在亞運會更進一步，跑出新的個人最佳13秒42。<br />\n記者：徐嘉華<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180826/58610878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F58610878&d=Y%2FW%2FCsZJIoYQ15%2FbMY8nJxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=70a10025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180826%2F58610878&h=7140a2de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180826/58610878</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港運動員唔係垃圾"}]}